  "title": "Three bright blue star-like UFOs hovered over Curitiba for 20 min [2002]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/11/a-bright-blue-star-like-ufo-hovered-over-curitiba-for-20-min-2002/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-jr",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>JUNE 16th, 2002</strong>. Time: 6:30 pm. Duration: 20 minutes. In Alto da XV district, city of Curitiba, State of Parana, a witness saw three (3) unidentified flying objects shaped like bright blue stars. The UFOs, according to the witness&#8217; report, were stationary in a region south of the city center of Curitiba. The sighting of the two UFOs was carried out under conditions of visibility described as &#8220;good&#8221; from the center of the city. There were no records of trails or signs of condensation left in the displacement of the sighted objects.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo &#8216;Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)&#8217;. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.625. &#8220;</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário com relato sobre avistamento de ovni em Alto da XV, Curitiba, Estado do Paraná&#8221;. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our &#8216;Info&#8217; page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [&#8220;Código de Referência&#8221;] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span></p>\n",
